---

For FHEVM Examples Competition

This software includes examples demonstrating Fully Homomorphic Encryption
(FHE) smart contracts. These examples are provided as educational material
for the FHEVM Examples Competition.

All participants in the competition agree to:
- Proper attribution of original work
- Following this license terms
- Using these examples for educational and development purposes only
- Not using for malicious or unauthorized purposes

Zama Confidential Blockchain Protocol
Copyright (c) 2024-2025 Zama

