Additional Notes:

1. OPEN SOURCE
   This project is open source and contributions are welcome. Please ensure
   any contributions adhere to this license.

2. DISCLAIMER OF WARRANTY
   This software is provided as-is. While Zama strives to maintain security
   and correctness, there are no warranties or guarantees of any kind.

   Users must conduct their own security audits before deploying to production.

3. NO GUARANTEE OF FHE SECURITY
   While FHEVM uses industry-leading FHE technology, users must understand
   the cryptographic assumptions and limitations of FHE before deployment.

4. USAGE IN PRODUCTION
   Before using this code in production:
   - Conduct thorough security audits
   - Test extensively on testnets
   - Review all cryptographic assumptions
   - Understand gas costs and performance implications
   - Follow all regulatory requirements

5. MODIFICATIONS
   Users may modify this software for their own use, but modifications
   must retain this license and copyright notice.

6. DISTRIBUTION
   Distributions of modified versions must:
   - Include this license
   - Document modifications
   - Retain copyright notices
   - Not misrepresent the original authors

7. ATTRIBUTION
   When using examples from this project, proper attribution is required:
   "Based on FHEVM Examples from the Zama FHEVM Examples Competition"

